{"tid":1118071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡6教堂酒店連環爆炸 逾160人死360傷","createTime":"2019-04-21T06:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T10:38:40.000Z","uid":15564,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"15880b5b705e39e6f67a32132fba2c28a67b2e1f","tid":1118071,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1484019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1484019%2F&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5ROoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=30e52b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1484019%2F&h=346df8aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1484019/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190421/_2019042113054963214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190421%2F_2019042113054963214.jpg&h=7d7fbfb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆炸後教堂內多人倒地受傷，現場一片頹垣敗瓦。網圖</span><br />\n斯里蘭卡至少3間教堂及3間酒店，在當地早上先後發生爆炸，死亡人數增加至超過160人死逾360傷。暫未有組織或個人宣稱對爆炸負責。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指，共有6處點爆炸，包括3間教堂及3間酒店 ,其中一間爆炸的教堂位於首都科倫坡，另一間位於科倫坡以北，造成至少50人死逾200人受傷。消息指爆炸時，教堂正進行復活節彌撒，傷者中包括有遊客。網上的相片顯示教堂內多人倒地受傷，現場一片頹垣敗瓦。<br />\n<br />\n印度媒體報道，爆炸發生後，斯里蘭卡政府軍部署了200名士兵。斯里蘭卡總理維克勒馬辛哈召開緊急會議，機場亦暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐斯里蘭卡使館已經啟動應急機制，正在核實是否有中國公民在爆炸中傷亡，並提醒在斯中國公民注意人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：13:01<br />\n更新時間：14:34<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190421/_2019042113080620665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190421%2F_2019042113080620665.jpg&h=846907c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">教堂內多人受傷。網圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190421/_2019042113430725939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190421%2F_2019042113430725939.jpg&h=ce5e93f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其中一間教堂爆炸後警方封鎖現場。AP</span>"},{"pid":"2cfc5a7772983979c323c2a5633d5760d5ce2c25","tid":1118071,"uid":35468,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"穆斯林殺耶教徒 --&gt; 冇人理"},{"pid":"16433c8dd7f998e58133231ff1bfd8167c7e507a","tid":1118071,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fff249668fcb368cbdcf8aaefa25e1677100a9","tid":1118071,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"十字軍東征"},{"pid":"60754507b459fa91f4012eb58a8c06670c46d8ce","tid":1118071,"uid":1761,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2cfc5a7772983979c323c2a5633d5760d5ce2c25","tid":1118071,"uid":35468,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"穆斯林殺耶教徒 --&gt; 冇人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"child登仔識撚分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dc764cf1ffbf10dd13174bf777f05f1895535a","tid":1118071,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9ab62713bdf8bf8552afd0f26aacc28e3cbf82","tid":1118071,"uid":202045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"咁似個套 孟買酒店嘅？"},{"pid":"4c8c4d5bcf14523233af3b541e940401c1095d0e